or_woodyallen_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_ewanmcgregor_woodyallen_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_ewanmcgregor_woodyallen_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_ewanmcgregor_woodyallen_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/2024_ewanmcgregor_woodyallen_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ewan-mcgregor">伊万·麦格雷戈</a>谈到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/woody-allen">伍迪·艾伦</a>曾在 2007 年犯罪惊悚片<em>《卡桑德拉之梦》</em>片场告诉他，他“让每个人都无聊得要死”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/trainspotting-genius-cult-film-1960605">《猜火车》：这部邪教电影及其续集的口述历史</a></strong></li></ul><p>在这部电影中，这位<em>《猜火车》</em>明星与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/colin-farrell">科林·法雷尔</a>合作，导演在片场给了麦格雷戈一些剪辑反馈。</p><p> “有一次，他走到我面前说，‘我能听到电影院里每个座位都在震动’，好像我把每个人都烦死了，然后每个人都离开了，”麦格雷戈在接受<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/features/ewan-mcgregor-star-wars-obi-wan-kenobi-walk-of-fame-1236140235/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》杂志</em></a>的新采访时回忆道。</p><p> “我当时想，‘哦，谢谢，伍迪。’所以我和科林·法雷尔一见面，我们就开始排队，因为有很大的长场景，而他不喜欢做报道，或者不经常做报道——作为一个演员，这样做真是太棒了。演员，因为这有点像在舞台上，但你必须跟上节奏。” </p><p><iframe title="卡桑德拉的梦想|预告片|科林·法瑞尔主演" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S1KW_e8GPOQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>尽管受到批评，艾伦的电影还是收到了褒贬不一的评价，<a href="https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/cassandras_dream" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>烂番茄</em></a>上的支持率仅为 46%。</p><p>与此同时，麦格雷戈将于今天晚些时候（9 月 12 日）在好莱坞星光大道上获得一颗星星。 “如果有人因为某件事而给你颁奖，你会感到非常高兴，”麦格雷戈说。</p><p> “你总是很高兴被人想到。但我不知道我的感受如何...<br />显然非常高兴、荣幸和感激，但也有点尴尬。”</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/woody-allen-premiere-interrupted-by-protesters-chanting-no-rape-culture-3493457">艾伦的电影<em>《致命一击》</em>的首映式最近被抗议者打断</a>，抗议者敦促威尼斯电影节“关掉对强奸犯的关注”。他们引用了导演伍迪·艾伦、吕克·贝松和罗曼·波兰斯基的例子，他们都被指控性虐待。</p><p>艾伦最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/woody-allen-calls-cancel-culture-silly-maintains-innocence-sexual-abuse-allegations-3493112">对养女迪伦·法罗的性虐待指控坚称自己无罪</a>，认为这些指控“没有根据”。导演一直否认这些指控，也从未在本案中被指控犯罪。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ewan-mcgregor-remembers-woody-allen-telling-him-he-was-boring-everyone-to-death-in-film-scene-3793058">伊万·麦格雷戈 (Ewan McGregor) 记得伍迪·艾伦 (Woody Allen) 在电影场景中告诉他，他“让每个人都无聊得要死”</a>的帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
诺埃尔·加拉格尔和曼城推出全新“Definitely City”球衣https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-and-man-city-launch-new-definitely-city-kit-3793062?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=noel-gallagher-and-man-城市推出新的肯定城市套件Liberty DunworthThu, 12 Sep 2024 10:03:40 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3793062 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该系列还包括运动夹克、飞行员夹克、T 恤等</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-and-man-city-launch-new-definitely-city-kit-3793062">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 和曼城 (Man City) 推出全新“Definitely City”球衣</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Definitely-Maybe-Man-City@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔</a>再次与曼城联手，这一次分享了一套以“Definitely Maybe”为灵感的新球衣。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-2025-reunion-tour-more-dates-rumoured-to-be-added-with-bonehead-reportedly-in-band-line-up-3788098">支持我：2025 年绿洲阵容中的所有球员</a></strong></li></ul><p>此次新合作是与 PUMA 新协议的一部分，这位英伦流行偶像和曼城队的终身粉丝帮助设计了一套球衣，球队将在 24/25 赛季的部分比赛中穿着。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">进行了改革，并宣布将在 2025 年举办现场演出，席卷全球</a>，此时 Oasis 正在庆祝<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">其突破性首张专辑《Definitely Maybe》发行 30 周年</a>。在新的设计中，该套件<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-shares-new-manchester-city-clothing-range-inspired-by-oasis-definitely-maybe-3789781">向立即可识别的专辑艺术作品致敬</a>。</p><p>在这套球衣中，特别版球衣采用浅稻草底色和大胆的蓝色侧幅。它还看到袖子的袖口和面板上有微妙的粉红色细节，以及海蓝色超声波的复杂轮廓。 </p><figure id="attachment_3793066" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3793066" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3793066" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design@2000x1270.jpg" alt="曼城、Puma 和 Noel Gallagher 设计的“Definitely City”球衣" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3793066" class="wp-caption-text">曼城、Puma 和 Noel Gallagher 设计的“Definitely City”球衣。图片来源：彪马</figcaption></figure><p>它将于 9 月 18 日在阿提哈德球场首次亮相，届时曼城队将迎战国际米兰队。从那时起，它将在本赛季余下的欧洲客场比赛中穿着。</p><p>该球衣也是更广泛的“Definitely Maybe”系列的一部分，该系列包括运动夹克和裤子、外套衬衫、飞行员夹克、T 恤、Polo 衫、复古球衣和斜纹上衣。请访问<a href="https://shop.mancity.com/en/definitely-city-collection/?utm_term=prospecting&amp;_gl=1*4kqskr*_gcl_au*NjExNjE1NTMuMTcyNjEzNTMyNg..*_ga*MTQ1MTY0MzQ4NC4xNzI2MTM1MzI2*_ga_83D496C6PL*MTcyNjEzNTMyNi4xLjEuMTcyNjEzNTMzMS41NS4wLjQxMjY5Njk3OQ..*_ga_QFRL9KTV4P*MTcyNjEzNTMyNi4xLjEuMTcyNjEzNTMyOC41OC4wLjA&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=mancity&amp;utm_content=web_story%3Futm_source%3Dmancity" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>了解更多信息。</p><p> “我比任何事情都更喜欢城市，在我进入音乐之前我就进入了城市，在我知道音乐是什么之前我就进入了城市。 “绝对可能”是我们走上这条路的原因，这个记录持续了很长时间，你无法预测这种事情。这是曼彻斯特工人阶级的伟大记录——这是真实的，”诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 谈到新的合作时说道。</p><p> “当 PUMA 在一场比赛中联系我们设计一套球衣时，我们花了大约五秒钟才同意。它与《Definitely Maybe》的封面采用相同的调色板：它很独特，但绝对引人注目，而且我认为它看起来很棒。当你看到代表你的俱乐部的人时，他们看起来不错很重要，”他补充道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="PUMA 与曼彻斯特城联手 NOEL GALLAGHER 推出 24/25 DEFINITELY CITY 球衣" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Zwa47D9vlRs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “‘绝对可能’对我来说从未失去它的魔力，我只是认为它是我们的精彩快照。在周年纪念日之际，我听它的次数比以往任何时候都多，这让我微笑——那是一段美好的时光。它催生了一套出色的足球装备，它的遗产将继续存在。”</p><p>球衣采用 100% 回收材料制成，不包括饰边和装饰，体现了 PUMA 对可持续发展的承诺。该系列的照片也是在按照《Definitely Maybe》封面重现的客厅中拍摄的，主演包括凯尔·沃克、杰西·帕克、马特奥·科瓦契奇和埃德森等曼城球员。</p><p> “24/25 Absolutely City 套装不仅仅是一件运动服；它也是一件运动服。”这是对曼城正在进行的旅程的庆祝，也是对与世界各地球迷产生共鸣的文化现象的致敬。”Marco Mueller（PUMA Teamsport Apparel 产品线管理高级主管）说道。 “我们将尖端技术与设计相结合，尊重俱乐部的传统和‘绝对可能’的传统。” </p><figure id="attachment_3793068" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3793068" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3793068" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design1@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design1@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design1@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design1@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design1@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design1@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/DM-Man-City-design1@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3793068" class="wp-caption-text">曼城、彪马和诺埃尔·加拉格尔设计的“Definitely City”球衣。图片来源：彪马</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3793072" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3793072" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3793072" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3793072" class="wp-caption-text">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 穿着“Definitely City”曼城 x PUMA 系列。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3793073" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3793073" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3793073" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City2@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City2@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City2@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City2@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City2@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NG-Man-City2@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3793073" class="wp-caption-text">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 穿着“Definitely City”曼城 x PUMA 系列。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>这并不是诺埃尔·加拉格尔第一次与他心爱的曼城合作。今年早些时候，这位歌手、词曲作者和吉他手还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-has-designed-the-font-for-the-new-man-city-kit-3766916">球队的主场球衣上设计了该字体</a>。</p><p>他用手写下球队的每个名字和号码，然后将笔迹转移到本赛季的杯短裤上，从而想出了这种字体。</p><p>尽管加拉格尔多年来一直直言不讳地表达了他对球队的支持，并且与球队有着悠久的历史，但今年早些时候，他被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-noel-gallagher-refuse-to-do-the-poznan-in-sea-of-celebrating-man-city-fans-3755532">发现拒绝在曼城球迷的庆祝活动中拒绝参加波兹南比赛，这确实</a>成为了头条新闻。</p><p>就在他观看曼城对阵富勒姆的比赛时，他的球队以 4-0 获胜，距离英超积分榜榜首又近了一步。然而，与视频中看到的一大群曼城球迷包围他不同的是，加拉格尔拒绝加入这一举动（球迷挽着手，转身离开球场并开始弹跳）。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Noel Gallagher 谈“议会天空”、人工智能绿洲、1975 年和英国脱欧" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?start=1630&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在因拒绝参加而被他的兄弟兼绿洲乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆</a>点名后，诺埃尔后来发表了一份声明<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/noel-gallagher-defends-not-doing-poznan-at-man-city-game-after-liam-calls-out-poor-behaviour-3755945">，解释说他没有参加，因为他“仍然感受到了一个相当精彩的夜晚的影响”</a> 。</p><p>在绿洲乐队的其他新闻中，乐队最近分享了他们期待已久的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">标志性首张专辑的重新发行</a>，但在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/consumer-champion-which-ticketmaster-refund-fans-oasis-reunion-tickets-3792128">粉丝们争先恐后地抢购他们即将举行的重聚演出的门票</a>后，乐队面临着强烈反对。</p><p>作为回应，乐队与销售期间引入的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-band-say-they-at-no-time-had-any-awareness-that-dynamic-pricing-was-going-to-be-used-3790679">大幅涨价保持了距离</a>，并宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-wembley-stadium-extra-reunion-dates-tickets-invite-only-no-surge-pricing-3790552">他们将在温布利举行两场额外的演出，但这一次对门票销售制定了更严格的规则</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-and-man-city-launch-new-definitely-city-kit-3793062">诺尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 和曼城 (Man City) 推出全新“Definitely City”球衣</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
